  "text": "The Kubernetes scheduler team's plan to rename `ScoreExtensions` interface to `ScoreNormalizer` and its accessor method `ScoreExtensions()` to `ScoreNormalizer()` will impact 19 Go source files across the kubernetes--v1.32.0 repository.\n\n## Interface Definition\n**File: pkg/scheduler/framework/interface.go** (lines 597-616)\n- Defines the `ScoreExtensions` interface with a single method `NormalizeScore()`\n- Defines the `ScorePlugin` interface which includes a `ScoreExtensions()` method that returns `ScoreExtensions`\n\n## Metrics Constant\n**File: pkg/scheduler/metrics/metrics.go** (lines 57, 74)\n- Defines the constant `ScoreExtensionNormalize = \"ScoreExtensionNormalize\"` used for metrics recording\n\n## Framework Runtime\n**File: pkg/scheduler/framework/runtime/framework.go** (lines 1171-1236)\n- Method `frameworkImpl.runScoreExtension()` calls `pl.ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()` to normalize scores\n- Uses `metrics.ScoreExtensionNormalize` constant for metrics observation\n\n## Plugin Implementations\nEight scoring plugins implement the `ScoreExtensions()` method:\n1. **ImageLocality** (pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/imagelocality/image_locality.go) - returns nil\n2. **NodeAffinity** (pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/nodeaffinity/node_affinity.go) - returns self and implements NormalizeScore()\n3. **InterPodAffinity** (pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/interpodaffinity/scoring.go) - returns self\n4. **BalancedAllocation** (pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/noderesources/balanced_allocation.go) - returns nil\n5. **Fit** (pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/noderesources/fit.go) - returns nil\n6. **PodTopologySpread** (pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/podtopologyspread/scoring.go) - returns self\n7. **TaintToleration** (pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/tainttoleration/taint_toleration.go) - returns self and implements NormalizeScore()\n8. **VolumeBinding** (pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/volumebinding/volume_binding.go) - returns nil\n\n## Test Files\nEight test files contain mock implementations or test calls to ScoreExtensions():\n1. **pkg/scheduler/framework/runtime/framework_test.go** - TestScoreWithNormalizePlugin, TestScorePlugin, TestPlugin\n2. **pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/interpodaffinity/scoring_test.go** - tests calling ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()\n3. **pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/nodeaffinity/node_affinity_test.go** - tests calling ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()\n4. **pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/tainttoleration/taint_toleration_test.go** - tests calling ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()\n5. **pkg/scheduler/schedule_one_test.go** - falseMapPlugin, numericMapPlugin, reverseNumericMapPlugin, trueMapPlugin\n6. **test/integration/scheduler/plugins/plugins_test.go** - ScorePlugin, ScoreWithNormalizePlugin\n7. **pkg/scheduler/testing/framework/fake_extender.go** - node2PrioritizerPlugin\n8. **pkg/scheduler/testing/framework/fake_plugins.go** - FakePreScoreAndScorePlugin\n\nThe migration requires updating the interface definition, all eight plugin implementations, the runtime framework call site, metrics constant naming, and all eight test files for a total of 19 files across the kubernetes--v1.32.0 repository."
}

